
** Scope of Alter System

  - spfile
  - memory
  - both


** Disable Triggers

  <example>
    -- disable system triggers
    alter system set "_system_trig_enabled"=false;
    @?/rdbms/admin/catalog
    @?/rdbms/admin/catproc
    -- re-enable system triggers
    alter system set "_system_trig_enabled"=true;
  </example>

** Show Checkpoints in Alert File

  <example>
    alter system set log_checkpoints_to_alert = TRUE;
  </example>


** Automatic Logging

  <example>
    SQL> alter syste archive log start; -- enable automatic archiving
    SQL> alter syste archive log stop;  -- disable automatic archiving
    SQL> alter syste archive log all;   -- manual archiving
  </example>

